A teenager has been seriously burnt after allegedly asking friends to wrap him in paper towels and set him alight in a Jackass-style prank.

Police were called to a home at Reynella East, south of Adelaide, early on Monday after paramedics reported that a man had been set on fire.

The 19-year-old man was at a friend's house when he allegedly asked to be wrapped in paper towel and set alight.

